room_title: Escape room "Framed" by Cipher Seeker Room Escape Challenge in New York
review: This was so much fun! We did the hardest room, and almost beat it! We were running a little late but they were really understanding about it. I highly recommend this place for anyone who likes these kinds of games and wants to try it in real life.

room_title: Escape room "Framed" by Cipher Seeker Room Escape Challenge in New York
review: Had great time! Took 12 and 14 year old and they want to do it every weekend now...staff was great and would highly recommend!

room_title: Escape room "Framed" by Cipher Seeker Room Escape Challenge in New York
review: Loved it! We went yesterday and it was so much fun! There was 4 of us and we did the framed room. The hour flew by and we had a great time proving our innocence. Will definitely be back!
